item.title: Automating The Network Redesign Process
item.author: contact@saggiehaim.net (Saggie Haim)
item.description: Namaste! I’m sitting in my hotel room, it’s very late, hoping not to get sick. It’s my first day in India, as my company has an office here in New Delhi. If you wonder why I hope not to get sick, well, this was my dinner today: Image of my indian dinner To be honest, it was very nice, not the best I had, but far from my worst one. If you didn’t notice, it had chicken inside.
